{{Top|leg}}
The mysterious '''base [[Starship/Legends|ship]]''' was sent to the [[Bastooine system/Legends|Orellon system]] by an extinct [[Alien/Legends|alien]] race centuries before the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]]. It was fully automated and manned by [[Wanderer Scout Surveyor|scout droids]] and [[87-RM Scout Collector|collector droids]] whose task it was to collect 30,000 unique specimens of alien life. Eventually, it reached [[Orellon II]] where its [[Droid/Legends|droids]] brought fear to the hearts of the local [[Kentra]]. Upon its arrival on Orellon II, it had received no messages from its [[Homeworld/Legends|homeworld]] in three hundred [[Standard year/Legends|years]]. The Kentra thought the droids were [[Voontragi|demons]], and commissioned a group of [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebels]] with the task of eliminating them. The ship was programmed to leave the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] and move on to the next if discovered or fired upon with energy weapons.

